(1796, 859, 'Conférence SFAF : « Piloter les actifs immatériels dans l’entreprise »', 'conference-sfaf-piloter-les-actifs-immateriels-dans-l-entreprise', '', '<p><em><strong><img style="margin-right: 5px; float: left;" src="images/stories/actualites/logo-SFAF.jpg" alt="logo-SFAF" width="150" height="105" />3° Conférence Annuelle Immatériel de la SFAF - Paris 15 mai 2014&nbsp;- une matinée</strong> </em><br /><br />La Société française des analystes financiers (SFAF) s’est donnée pour mission de sensibiliser l’ensemble des acteurs financiers à l’Immatériel. À l’occasion de sa 3e Conférence annuelle sur l’Immatériel, la SFAF propose un éclairage et un débat à partir d’une réflexion partagée et de retours d’expérience entre des acteurs de l’immatériel sur le pilotage des actifs immatériels au sein de l’entreprise.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>Date&nbsp;: <strong>jeudi 15 mai 2014, de 8 h 30 à 12 h 30</strong><br />Lieu : Auditorium Thomson Reuters INSERT INTO `jnew_content` (`id`, `asset_id`, `title`, `alias`, `title_alias`, `introtext`, `fulltext`, `state`, `sectionid`, `mask`, `catid`, `created`, `created_by`, `created_by_alias`, `modified`, `modified_by`, `checked_out`, `checked_out_time`, `publish_up`, `publish_down`, `images`, `urls`, `attribs`, `version`, `parentid`, `ordering`, `metakey`, `metadesc`, `access`, `hits`, `metadata`, `featured`, `language`, `xreference`) VALUES
(1272, 539, 'Jean-Pierre Corniou', 'jean-pierre-corniou', '', '<p><strong><span class="texte">Président de EDS Services</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><a class="spotlight" style="position: relative; overflow: hidden;" data-spotlight="on" data-lightbox="transitionIn:elastic;transitionOut:elastic;" href="images/stories/video/jamet.html"> <img class="size-auto" alt="temoignages corniou2" src="images/stories/temoignages/temoignages_corniou2.jpg" width="300" height="171" /></a></p>\r\n<div class="overlay" style="background-image: url(''images/yootheme/spotlight/button_play.png''); background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; position: absolute; visibility: visible; display: none; width: 440px; height: 250px; opacity: 0; top: 0px; left: 0px;"></div>\r\n<p class="spip"><img src="http://www.observatoire-immateriel.com/puce.gif" alt="-" width="10" height="5" />&nbsp;Vous avez été longtemps président du Cigref qui vient de publier une étude sur le capital immatériel. Quel lien faites vous entre Système d’information et Capital Immatériel&nbsp;?</p>\r\n<p class="spip"><img src="http://www.observatoire-immateriel.com/puce.gif" alt="-" width="10" height="5" />&nbsp;Lorsqu’on parle de capital immatériel, les premiers actifs cités sont&nbsp;: les clients, le capital humain, les brevets et les marques. Pensez-vous que la place des systèmes d’information est sous estimée au sein du capital immatériel&nbsp;?</p>\r\n<p class="spip"><img src="http://www.observatoire-immateriel.com/puce.gif" alt="-" width="10" height="5" />&nbsp;On peut s’attendre à ce que les systèmes d’information prennent une place croissante dans la définition du capital immatériel. En même temps, pour un grand nombre d’entreprise, l’informatique coûte trop cher. S<a data-lightbox="ON" href="images/stories/video/Corniou.flv">erait-ce la fin de cette époqu</a>e&nbsp;?</p>\r\n<p class="spip"><a data-lightbox="on" href="">voir la video</a></p>\r\n<p><a data-lightbox="on" href="images/stories/video/jamet.html" title="Flash Swf">Swf</a></p>', '', 0, 0, 0, 11, '2011-08-14 09:34:58', 62, '', '2013-09-12 09:33:34', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-08-14 09:34:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_section":"","link_section":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_vote":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_pdf_icon":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","language":"","keyref":"","readmore":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","link_author":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 26, 0, 2, '', '', 1, 0, '', 0, '*', ''),
(1273, 540, 'Georges Epinette', 'georges-epinette', '', '<p><strong><span class="texte">Directeur des Systèmes d’information du groupement des Mousquetaires et Administrateur du Cigref</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><a target="_blank" data-lightbox="width:320;height:278;transitionIn:elastic;transitionOut:elastic" class="spotlight" style="position: relative; overflow: hidden;" data-spotlight="on" href="images/stories/video/video_Epinette.swf"> <img class="size-auto" alt="temoignages epinette2" src="images/stories/temoignages/temoignages_epinette2.jpg" width="300" height="171" /></a></p>\r\n<div class="overlay" style="background-image: url(''images/yootheme/spotlight/button_play.png''); background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; position: absolute; visibility: visible; display: none; width: 440px; height: 250px; opacity: 0; top: 0px; left: 0px;"></div>\r\n<div class="texte_actus">\r\n<p class="spip"><img src="http://www.observatoire-immateriel.com/puce.gif" alt="-" width="10" height="5" />&nbsp;Vous avez pris une part importante aux travaux du Cigref sur le capital immatériel. Mais au sein de votre entreprise, quels sont les enjeux relatifs au capital système d’information.</p>\r\n<p class="spip"><img src="http://www.observatoire-immateriel.com/puce.gif" alt="-" width="10" height="5" />&nbsp;La tendance des entreprises à l’externalisation de leur informatique ne cesse de croître. Est-ce que le fait que le SI prenne une place importante dans le capital immatériel ne pourrait pas remettre en cause cette évolution&nbsp;?</p>\r\n<p class="spip"><img src="http://www.observatoire-immateriel.com/puce.gif" alt="-" width="10" height="5" />&nbsp;Selon vous est-ce que l’enjeu d’intégrer pleinement les TIC dans le capital immatériel concerne surtout le Directeur des Systèmes d’information ou le DG&nbsp;?</p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 11, '2011-08-14 09:36:02', 62, '', '2013-09-12 09:33:34', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-08-14 09:36:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_section":"","link_section":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_vote":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_pdf_icon":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","language":"","keyref":"","readmore":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","link_author":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 10, 0, 7, '', '', 1, 2188, '', 0, '*', ''),
(1274, 541, 'Françoise Guichard', 'francoise-guichard', '', '<p><strong><span class="texte">Directrice du Développement Durable de GDF</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><a class="spotlight" style="position: relative; overflow: hidden;" data-spotlight="on" data-lightbox="transitionIn:elastic;transitionOut:elastic;" href="http://vimeo.com/15261921?autoplay=true"> <img class="size-auto" alt="temoignages guichard2" src="images/stories/temoignages/temoignages_guichard2.jpg" width="300" height="171" /></a></p>\r\n<div class="overlay" style="background-image: url(''images/yootheme/spotlight/button_play.png''); background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; position: absolute; visibility: visible; display: none; width: 440px; height: 250px; opacity: 0; top: 0px; left: 0px;"></div>\r\n<p class="spip"><img src="http://www.observatoire-immateriel.com/puce.gif" alt="-" width="10" height="5" />&nbsp;Pourquoi vous êtes vous intéressée au capital immatériel&nbsp;?</p>\r\n<p class="spip"><img src="http://www.observatoire-immateriel.com/puce.gif" alt="-" width="10" height="5" />&nbsp;Et quelles sont vos opérations dans ce domaine&nbsp;?</p>', '', 0, 0, 0, 11, '2011-08-14 09:38:30', 62, '', '2013-09-12 09:33:34', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-08-14 09:38:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_section":"","link_section":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_vote":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_pdf_icon":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","language":"","keyref":"","readmore":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","link_author":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 6, 0, 8, '', '', 1, 0, '', 0, '*', ''),
(1275, 542, 'Marc-Antoine Jamet', 'marc-antoine-jamet', '', '<p><strong><span class="texte">Secrétaire général du Groupe LVMH, ancien Président de l’Union des fabricants (UNIFAB)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><a target="_blank" data-lightbox="width:320;height:278;transitionIn:elastic;transitionOut:elastic" class="spotlight" style="position: relative; overflow: hidden;" data-spotlight="on" href="images/stories/video/video_Jamet.swf"> <img class="size-auto" alt="temoignages jamet2" src="images/stories/temoignages/temoignages_jamet2.jpg" height="171" width="300" /></a></p>\r\n<div class="overlay" style="background-image: url(''images/yootheme/spotlight/button_play.png''); background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; position: absolute; visibility: visible; display: none; width: 440px; height: 250px; opacity: 0; top: 0px; left: 0px;"></div>\r\n<p class="spip"><img src="http://www.observatoire-immateriel.com/puce.gif" alt="-" height="5" width="10" /> Vous êtes le Président de l’Union des fabricants, qui sont vos adhérents ?</p>\r\n<p class="spip"><img src="http://www.observatoire-immateriel.com/puce.gif" alt="-" height="5" width="10" /> Toutes les entreprises investissent dans leur marque, mais à votre connaissance, combien d’entreprises mesure vraiment la valeur de leur marque et comment voyez vous l’avenir à cet égard ?</p>\r\n<p class="spip"><img src="http://www.observatoire-immateriel.com/puce.gif" alt="-" height="5" width="10" /> Pensez-vous que vos adhérents intègreront demain dans leur communication financière des informations sur le capital immatériel</p>\r\n<p class="spip">(<em>enregistrement effectué en 2009</em>)</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 11, '2011-08-14 09:39:17', 62, '', '2013-09-12 09:33:34', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-08-14 09:39:17', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_section":"","link_section":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_vote":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_pdf_icon":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","language":"","keyref":"","readmore":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","link_author":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 10, 0, 6, '', '', 1, 2316, '', 0, '*', ''),
(1276, 543, 'Olivier Mélis', 'olivier-melis', '', '<p><strong><span class="texte">Membre du directoire de Norauto</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><a target="_blank" data-lightbox="width:320;height:278;transitionIn:elastic;transitionOut:elastic" class="spotlight" style="position: relative; overflow: hidden;" data-spotlight="on" href="images/stories/video/video_Melis.swf"> <img class="size-auto" alt="temoignages melis2" src="images/stories/temoignages/temoignages_melis2.jpg" width="300" height="170" /></a></p>\r\n<div class="overlay" style="background-image: url(''images/yootheme/spotlight/button_play.png''); background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; position: absolute; visibility: visible; display: none; width: 440px; height: 250px; opacity: 0; top: 0px; left: 0px;"></div>\r\n<div class="texte_actus">\r\n<p class="spip"><img src="http://www.observatoire-immateriel.com/puce.gif" alt="-" width="10" height="5" />&nbsp;Pourquoi vous êtes vous intéressé au capital immatériel&nbsp;?</p>\r\n<p class="spip"><img src="http://www.observatoire-immateriel.com/puce.gif" alt="-" width="10" height="5" />&nbsp;Comment vous y prenez-vous&nbsp;?</p>\r\n<p class="spip"><img src="http://www.observatoire-immateriel.com/puce.gif" alt="-" width="10" height="5" />&nbsp;Avez-vous mise en place un outils de pilotage de vos actifs immatériels&nbsp;?</p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 11, '2011-08-14 09:40:52', 62, '', '2013-09-12 09:33:34', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-08-14 09:40:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_intro":"","show_section":"","link_section":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_vote":"","show_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_pdf_icon":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","language":"","keyref":"","readmore":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","link_author":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","alter