Supérieur de l''Ordre des Experts-Comptables (CSOEC)</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial; min-height: 21px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;"><strong>• Dominique Blanc</strong> –&nbsp; Directeur R&amp;D Novethic</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial; min-height: 21px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;"><strong>• Danielle Bourlange</strong> –&nbsp; Directrice de l’APIE</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial; min-height: 21px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;"><strong>• Thibault Bouvier</strong> – Président Input IP</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;"><strong>• André Braud</strong> - R&amp;D, études RH Auchan</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;">• <strong>Eric Carreel</strong> - Withings</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial; min-height: 21px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial; min-height: 21px;"><strong>• Thomas Couaillet</strong> –&nbsp; Directeur PI Nutriset</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial; min-height: 21px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;"><strong>• Carole Couvert</strong>&nbsp;– Présidente CFE-CGC</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;"><strong>• Xavier Crouan</strong> - Directeur Général de la Communication de la Région Île-de-France</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial; min-height: 21px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;"><strong>• Daniel Delorge </strong>– Associé du cabinet Valopt,&nbsp; Membre du bureau de l’OI</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;"><strong>• Patrick de Cambourg</strong> - Président de l''Autorité des Normes Comptables, Président d''honneur de Mazars</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial; min-height: 21px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;"><strong>• Clément de Souza</strong>&nbsp;– Délégué National Centre des Jeunes Dirigeants D’entreprise</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;"><strong>• Jean-Philippe Desmartin</strong> - Senior Analyst, Head of ESG Research Oddo Securities<span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-style: normal;"><em><span style="font-size: 8.0pt; font-family: Verdana; mso-fareast-font-family: ''MS Mincho''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-ansi-language: FR; mso-fareast-language: JA;"><span style="color: gray;"><br /></span></span></em></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;"><strong>• Joëlle Durieux</strong> - Directrice Générale de France Innovation</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial; min-height: 21px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;"><strong>• Alban Eral</strong>&nbsp;– Directeur du pôle Stratégies d''Innovation AXESSIO</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial; min-height: 21px;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial;"><strong>• Alan Fustec</strong> – Président de Goodwill Management, Directeur Scientifique de l''OI